a\"}, {\"begin\": 777, \"end\": 785, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"score\": 0.9999999999413376, \"rank\": 5.869530734172769e-11, \"text\": \"Tahitian\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the oceanand\", \"from\": 622, \"to\": 634}, {\"ngram\": \"the lush green mountains\", \"from\": 647, \"to\": 671}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 683, \"to\": 692}, {\"ngram\": \"Visitors\", \"from\": 737, \"to\": 745}, {\"ngram\": \"dancing\", \"from\": 795, \"to\": 802}, {\"ngram\": \"ceremonies\", \"from\": 807, \"to\": 817}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Local government, Olympics and surfing officials had hand-woven palms placed around their necks upon arrival.\", \"from\": 819, \"to\": 928, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Local government\", \"from\": 819, \"to\": 835}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympics\", \"from\": 837, \"to\": 845}, {\"ngram\": \"surfing officials\", \"from\": 850, \"to\": 867}, {\"ngram\": \"hand-woven palms\", \"from\": 872, \"to\": 888}, {\"ngram\": \"their necks\", \"from\": 903, \"to\": 914}, {\"ngram\": \"arrival\", \"from\": 920, \"to\": 927}]}, {\"sentence\": \"White tents provided a shady spot for vendors to sell local vegetables, Polynesian crafts and food.\", \"from\": 929, \"to\": 1028, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1001, \"end\": 1011, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesia\", \"score\": 0.9944872030281784, \"rank\": 0.0028371234133744414, \"text\": \"Polynesian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"White tents\", \"from\": 929, \"to\": 940}, {\"ngram\": \"a shady spot\", \"from\": 950, \"to\": 962}, {\"ngram\": \"vendors\", \"from\": 967, \"to\": 974}, {\"ngram\": \"local vegetables\", \"from\": 983, \"to\": 999}, {\"ngram\": \"food\", \"from\": 1023, \"to\": 1027}]}, {\"sentence\": \"During one part of the ceremony athletes sealed banana leaves into a vessel, following an ancestral tradition in Polynesian culture - called Rahiri - used as a prelude to important events to secure the peace and union of those competing.\", \"from\": 1030, \"to\": 1267, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1143, \"end\": 1161, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesia\", \"score\": 0.9925769045997705, \"rank\": 0.007478609834417903, \"text\": \"Polynesian culture\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"one part\", \"from\": 1037, \"to\": 1045}, {\"ngram\": \"the ceremony athletes\", \"from\": 1049, \"to\": 1070}, {\"ngram\": \"banana leaves\", \"from\": 1078, \"to\": 1091}, {\"ngram\": \"a vessel\", \"from\": 1097, \"to\": 1105}, {\"ngram\": \"an ancestral tradition\", \"from\": 1117, \"to\": 1139}, {\"ngram\": \"a prelude\", \"from\": 1188, \"to\": 1197}, {\"ngram\": \"important events\", \"from\": 1201, \"to\": 1217}, {\"ngram\": \"the peace\", \"from\": 1228, \"to\": 1237}, {\"ngram\": \"union\", \"from\": 1242, \"to\": 1247}]}, {\"sentence\": \"During another part of the ceremony, athletes from different countries poured sand into a single communal container, symbolizing unity and respect for the ocean.\", \"from\": 1268, \"to\": 1429, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"another part\", \"from\": 1275, \"to\": 1287}, {\"ngram\": \"the ceremony\", \"from\": 1291, \"to\": 1303}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 1305, \"to\": 1313}, {\"ngram\": \"different countries\", \"from\": 1319, \"to\": 1338}, {\"ngram\": \"sand\", \"from\": 1346, \"to\": 1350}, {\"ngram\": \"a single communal container\", \"from\": 1356, \"to\": 1383}, {\"ngram\": \"unity\", \"from\": 1397, \"to\": 1402}, {\"ngram\": \"respect\", \"from\": 1407, \"to\": 1414}, {\"ngram\": \"the ocean\", \"from\": 1419, \"to\": 1428}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Before the event, surfer Caroline Marks from the United States said she was excited to be returning to the Olympics after she placed fourth at the Tokyo Olympics, where Olympic surfing first debuted.\", \"from\": 1431, \"to\": 1630, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1456, \"end\": 1470, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caroline_Marks\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Caroline Marks\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caroline_Marks\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caroline_Marks\"}, {\"begin\": 1480, \"end\": 1493, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.999999973756076, \"rank\": 2.592376606496239e-08, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 1438, \"to\": 1447}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1534, \"to\": 1546}, {\"ngram\": \"the Tokyo Olympics\", \"from\": 1574, \"to\": 1592}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic surfing\", \"from\": 1600, \"to\": 1615}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This is way different from Tokyo, when we were in pandemic and there were no spectators - it felt secluded,\\\" she told AP.\", \"from\": 1632, \"to\": 1754, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1660, \"end\": 1665, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9997564052904813, \"rank\": 0.00015835691235020782, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1751, \"end\": 1753, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.99993570360248, \"rank\": 6.429605571207522e-05, \"text\": \"AP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no spectators\", \"from\": 1707, \"to\": 1720}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This Olympics definitely have a different vibe and it's great to be back.\\\"\", \"from\": 1755, \"to\": 1830, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This Olympics\", \"from\": 1756, \"to\": 1769}, {\"ngram\": \"a different vibe\", \"from\": 1786, \"to\": 1802}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The event was open to the public, with locals and tourists alike attending.\", \"from\": 1832, \"to\": 1907, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The event\", \"from\": 1832, \"to\": 1841}, {\"ngram\": \"the public\", \"from\": 1854, \"to\": 1864}, {\"ngram\": \"locals\", \"from\": 1871, \"to\": 1877}, {\"ngram\": \"tourists\", \"from\": 1882, \"to\": 1890}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think it's a really great opportunity for us to show our culture to the world and really demonstrate that we exist,\\\" said local guesthouse owner Hiro Boosie, 25.\", \"from\": 1909, \"to\": 2073, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2057, \"end\": 2061, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hiro_Nakamura\", \"score\": 0.9999478328851745, \"rank\": 4.844116661124983e-05, \"text\": \"Hiro\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hiro_Nakamura\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hiro_Nakamura\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a really great opportunity\", \"from\": 1923, \"to\": 1949}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1954, \"to\": 1956}, {\"ngram\": \"our culture\", \"from\": 1965, \"to\": 1976}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1980, \"to\": 1989}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We want to show what kind of people we are to the world.\\\"\", \"from\": 2074, \"to\": 2132, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"what kind\", \"from\": 2091, \"to\": 2100}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 2104, \"to\": 2110}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 2121, \"to\": 2130}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite extra security such as police checkpoints and some road closures closer to the Olympic venues, tourists said that they felt their visit to Tahiti during the Olympics was so far a smooth and welcoming experience.\", \"from\": 2134, \"to\": 2353, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2281, \"end\": 2287, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"score\": 0.9997136354501387, \"rank\": 0.0002864465782022465, \"text\": \"Tahiti\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"extra security\", \"from\": 2142, \"to\": 2156}, {\"ngram\": \"police checkpoints\", \"from\": 2165, \"to\": 2183}, {\"ngram\": \"some road closures\", \"from\": 2188, \"to\": 2206}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic venues\", \"from\": 2217, \"to\": 2235}, {\"ngram\": \"tourists\", \"from\": 2237, \"to\": 2245}, {\"ngram\": \"their visit\", \"from\": 2266, \"to\": 2277}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2295, \"to\": 2307}, {\"ngram\": \"a smooth and welcoming experience\", \"from\": 2319, \"to\": 2352}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The locals are amazing, and I feel that it's actually very well organized for tourists to be here,\\\" said Dhikra Bahri, 23, who was visiting from Tunisia.\", \"from\": 2355, \"to\": 2509, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2468, \"end\": 2473, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bahri_dynasty\", \"score\": 0.9999993919129367, \"rank\": 6.080874397016204e-07, \"text\": \"Bahri\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bahri_dynasty\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bahri_dynasty\"}, {\"begin\": 2501, \"end\": 2508, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tunisia\", \"score\": 0.9981800948803216, \"rank\": 0.0018136942775829154, \"text\": \"Tunisia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tunisia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tunisia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The locals\", \"from\": 2356, \"to\": 2366}, {\"ngram\": \"tourists\", \"from\": 2434, \"to\": 2442}]}, {\"sentence\": \"International Surfing Association president Fernando Aguerre announced that the surfing competition would start the following day.Surf forecasts predictthe conditions will be favorable.\", \"from\": 2511, \"to\": 2696, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2511, \"end\": 2544, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Surfing_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Surfing Association\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Surfing_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Surfing_Association\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the surfing competition\", \"from\": 2587, \"to\": 2610}, {\"ngram\": \"Surf\", \"from\": 2641, \"to\": 2645}, {\"ngram\": \"predictthe conditions\", \"from\": 2656, \"to\": 2677}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Only four days of a 10-day window will be allotted for the competition, dependent upon wave conditions.\", \"from\": 2697, \"to\": 2800, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Only four days\", \"from\": 2697, \"to\": 2711}, {\"ngram\": \"a 10-day window\", \"from\": 2715, \"to\": 2730}, {\"ngram\": \"the competition\", \"from\": 2752, \"to\": 2767}, {\"ngram\": \"wave conditions\", \"from\": 2784, \"to\": 2799}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Throughout the week, competitors were seen paddling out to the world-famous waves of Teahupo'o starting before sunrise to take advantage of exclusive access to the location for training ahead of the competition.\", \"from\": 2802, \"to\": 3013, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the week\", \"from\": 2813, \"to\": 2821}, {\"ngram\": \"competitors\", \"from\": 2823, \"to\": 2834}, {\"ngram\": \"the world-famous waves\", \"from\": 2861, \"to\": 2883}, {\"ngram\": \"sunrise\", \"from\": 2913, \"to\": 2920}, {\"ngram\": \"advantage\", \"from\": 2929, \"to\": 2938}, {\"ngram\": \"exclusive access\", \"from\": 2942, \"to\": 2958}, {\"ngram\": \"the location\", \"from\": 2962, \"to\": 2974}, {\"ngram\": \"training\", \"from\": 2979, \"to\": 2987}, {\"ngram\": \"the competition\", \"from\": 2997, \"to\": 3012}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In Teahupo'o, residents have spent the final days before the competition preparing their town for the influx of extra people: Families have cleaned trash and debris from beachside walking paths, extended their business hours and building homemade dirt road bumps.\", \"from\": 3015, \"to\": 3278, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"residents\", \"from\": 3029, \"to\": 3038}, {\"ngram\": \"the final days\", \"from\": 3050, \"to\": 3064}, {\"ngram\": \"the competition\", \"from\": 3072, \"to\": 3087}, {\"ngram\": \"their town\", \"from\": 3098, \"to\": 3108}, {\"ngram\": \"the influx\", \"from\": 3113, \"to\": 3123}, {\"ngram\": \"extra people\", \"from\": 3127, \"to\": 3139}, {\"ngram\": \"Families\", \"from\": 3141, \"to\": 3149}, {\"ngram\": \"trash\", \"from\": 3163, \"to\": 3168}, {\"ngram\": \"debris\", \"from\": 3173, \"to\": 3179}, {\"ngram\": \"beachside walking paths\", \"from\": 3185, \"to\": 3208}, {\"ngram\": \"their business hours\", \"from\": 3219, \"to\": 3239}, {\"ngram\": \"dirt road bumps\", \"from\": 3262, \"to\": 3277}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 2024 surfing event sets the Olympic record for the competition held furthest away from a host city.\", \"from\": 3280, \"to\": 3383, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The 2024 surfing event\", \"from\": 3280, \"to\": 3302}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic record\", \"from\": 3308, \"to\": 3326}, {\"ngram\": \"the competition\", \"from\": 3331, \"to\": 3346}, {\"ngram\": \"a host city\", \"from\": 3371, \"to\": 3382}]}, {\"sentence\": \"___ AP Summer Olympics:https://apnews.com/hub/2024-paris-olympic-games\", \"from\": 3384, \"to\": 3455, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}]}"